tensor->nb[0] = ggml_type_size(type);
tensor->nb[1] = ggml_row_size(type, tensor->ne[0]);
tensor->nb[2] = tensor->nb[1] * tensor->ne[1];
tensor->nb[3] = tensor->nb[2] * tensor->ne[2];
```

`src/llama-kv-cache-dkvt.h` L11–18 — type mapping:
```
dkvt_tg_type_k: TURBO4_0/TURBO2_0 → GGML_TYPE_F16
dkvt_tg_type_v: TURBO4_0/TURBO2_0 → GGML_TYPE_Q8_0
